high_descs: Turn around to stand at the  counter just left of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the sharp knife with yellow handle from the counter.
Turn back around and carry the knife across the room to the counter space left of the fridge.
Use the knife to slice the apple on the counter.
Turn back around and carry the knife to the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn around again, and return to the sliced apple on the counter left of the fridge.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Carry the slice of apple to the fridge on your right.
Place the apple slice inside and then remove once cold.
Turn and carry the apple slice to the counter where you left the knife above the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of apple on the counter by the dishwasher.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter that is left of the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left, go past the counter, hang a right, go to the counter where the apple and tomato is.
Cut the apple that is on the counter into slices.
Turn to the right, go to the fridge, hang a right, go to the counter across the room.
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the bread.
Turn around, go past the counter, hang a left, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter where the apple is.
Pick up a slice of the apple from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the fridge on the left.
Put the apple inside the fridge and close the door, remove the apple from the fridge once it is cold.
Go to the left, go forward, hang a left and go to the counter where the knife is.
Put the slice of apple on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put cold apple on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the counter near the sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the counter on the other side of the kitchen
Cut the apple
Go to the counter near the dishwasher
Put the knife down on the counter
Go to the counter on the other side of the kitchen
Pick up an apple slice
Go to the fridge
Chill the apple
Go to the counter near the dishwasher
Put the apple down near the knife
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple slice on the counter
